    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
               
	<pb facs="liv_001082_0001" n="0001"/>
<lb/><opener><dateline rend="right"><placeName>Drumcondra Castle</placeName>
<lb/><date when="1857-08-22">28<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi> August
<lb/>1857</date></dateline><add place="marginleft" hand="U" rend="blue">18</add><!-- this page number is circled, but doesn't fall under query's usage. What should I do? BL-->
<lb/>   
<lb/><salute>My Dear Brother</salute></opener>
<lb/><p>As there is
<lb/>scarce time between
<lb/>this and the publication
<lb/>I think we can wait
<lb/>and I shall consult
<lb/><persName>Murray</persName> as he
<lb/>intended the <placeName>Falls</placeName>
<lb/>for the beginning of
<lb/>the Book.

	<pb facs="liv_001082_0002" n="0002"/>
<lb/>Please send me
<lb/>at once a sheet
<lb/>or two containing
<lb/>the explanation
<lb/>of the difference
<lb/>of amount of
<lb/>rain south &amp;
<lb/>North of the Equator
<lb/>the sheet contains
<lb/>a note by <persName>Babinet</persName>
<lb/>the Frenchman - He
<lb/>alter <!-- could be "after" or "other" potentially. BL--> a note by

	<pb facs="liv_001082_0003" n="0003"/>
<lb/><persName>Gabriel</persName> &amp; <persName>Brand</persName>
<lb/>I need them for
<lb/>my Mondays speech
<lb/>Will leave on
<lb/>Monday night in
<lb/>order to be of
<lb/><persName>Captain <unclear>Frothers</unclear></persName>
<lb/>wrote <persName>Mary<unclear>this</unclear></persName><!-- whole word here looks like "Marythis", don't know what to put. BL-->
<lb/>mommy.<space extent="1" unit="words"/>1400
<lb/>tickets of admission
<lb/>have been bought
<lb/>in <placeName>Dublin</placeName>. The
<lb/>Berliana<!-- tried my best here, unsure if correct. BL--> need
<lb/><unclear>davie</unclear> may be

	<pb facs="liv_001082_0004" n="0004"/>
<lb/>put in where the
<lb/><term type="tribe">Makololo</term> dance is
<lb/>described -- the
<lb/><term type="animal">Buffalo</term> is mentioned
<lb/>on the <placeName><geogName type="river">Leanubye</geogName></placeName><!--going by letters alone I'm close, but can't find info online if I'm write. Seems familiar, but unsure. BL--> &amp;<add place="above">near Seslieke</add><!--same with this "Seslieke". Right on letters, no info found online. -->
<lb/>again below
<lb/><placeName>Upendes</placeName> or <placeName>Bosowa</placeName>
<lb/>if I succeed in getting
<lb/>to <persName>Captain Frothers</persName>
<lb/>on tuesday I would
<lb/>sleep at <unclear>MS Taylor</unclear><!-- it is actually legible, but I can't figure out what it is, need context. BL-->
<lb/>&amp; then join you at
<lb/>Helen's on Wednesday.
</p><!-- there is actually no visible closer, leaving as is. BL-->


